OL,3,CPolice make record number of arrests
OL,4,Cduring FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,FThe highest number of arrests within
OL,7,Fsix weeks of the World Cup have been
OL,8,Fmade in the West Midlands since
OL,9,Frecords began.
OL,11,FAfter England's semi-final match with
OL,12,FArgentina on Wednesday 15 July, 226
OL,13,Farrests were made within 24-hours.
OL,15,FBetween 10pm and 3am post match, the
OL,16,Fpolice received 1,083 calls into their
OL,17,Femergency call room.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
