OL,3,CPolice make record number of arrests
OL,4,Cduring FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,FSince the start of the football
OL,7,Ftournament, West Midlands Police made
OL,8,Fan average of 188 arrests per day -
OL,9,Fthe highest number since the force's
OL,10,Frecords began.
OL,12,FLyndsey Bailey Smith from West
OL,13,FMidlands Police said: "We have seen a
OL,14,Fsignificant increase in calls during
OL,15,Fthe World Cup and especially post
OL,16,FEngland matches.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
